Please download and have a look! You will need Processing 1.0 to run this.
Download it here: http://processing.org/download/

The ruby code can be run with ruby-processing. First do
  sudo gem install ruby-processing
and then run it with
  rp5 run flowhan.rb

The program is showing some a small graph of Chinese characters that arrange by themselves.